content: I think I'll use Google Sheets for my spreadsheet. Can you help me figure out how to calculate the total value of my collection? I have a mix of vintage and limited edition dolls, and I'd like to get an estimated value for insurance purposes. By the way, speaking of limited editions, I just got a vintage 1960s Barbie doll last weekend that I've been searching for months, and it's still in mint condition with its original packaging and accessories.
